{"tid":1227560,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"我求求大家聽日一定要和平","createTime":"2019-06-15T15:16:41.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-19T02:57:44.000Z","uid":259302,"like":66,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":18,"replies":[{"pid":"7ce05dc4a28465985c21e010fe42c5aa021295bb","tid":1227560,"uid":259302,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-15T15:16:41.000Z","msg":"烈士已經出現左，我都好憤怒，但大家一定要<span style=\"color: blue;\">冷靜</span>，聽日好多人一家大細出，好多人甚至係睇完9／6同12／6先開始轉軑，佢地係和理非，唔會衝，亦衝唔起，本來講左和理非遊行，<span style=\"color: red;\">我地衝會再次分化和理非同勇武</span>，唔好忘記12／6嘅小成功係和理非同勇武合作嘅結果，一旦分化，和理非係緊急關頭無制止力，勇武無左群眾基礎比嘅合理性，<span style=\"color: red;\">大家一盤散沙，我地就玩完</span>。呢個係長爭抗爭，聽日大家先和理非，紀念烈士，<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">君子之仇，十年未晚！</span></strong></span>"},{"pid":"349150d326ba7096fee165b347b537dd4dbf06ac","tid":1227560,"uid":212182,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-15T15:17:20.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"3f5177289cf300eb734a5d856b4d57b2939b26a6","tid":1227560,"uid":72497,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-15T15:17:33.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"19d9c2cd1817dd00b7137b0e12f59287f6c7190e","tid":1227560,"uid":259302,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-15T15:20:27.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"bc5c65756df72d866bc97a96f2f214234c5a7082","tid":1227560,"uid":83789,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-15T15:23:06.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"b2ec6abdecc19001c424562b029dd1a95b18804d","tid":1227560,"uid":248019,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-15T15:24:13.000Z","msg":"一定要和平！"},{"pid":"ef9056209ef80d8cbff5878126786b5a9328f62b","tid":1227560,"uid":260370,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-15T15:26:41.000Z","msg":"我係612夢見立會示威區既勇武，<br />\n<br />\n616還是和平進行吧，<br />\n當做為烈士默哀。<br />\n<br />\n因為我實在太悲怒，<br />\n需要時間來沉澱自己，<br />\n不然真的會失控。"},{"pid":"a9de6a6d2585c00a7d8ee0c3d822f2d634adc4fb","tid":1227560,"uid":259302,"li